      • findMatchTextIndex

        public static int findMatchTextIndex(java.lang.String text,
                     java.lang.String pattern,
                     int occurrencePosition)
        Searches the text for the occurrence of a pattern.
        Parameters:
        text - examined text
        pattern - search pattern text
        occurrencePosition - occurrence position where the pattern must be found (1, 2, ..). 0 (zero) == find all patterns
        Returns:
        -1, if the pattern was not found (at the given occurrencePosition), otherwise the index (char offset) where the pattern was found. For "find all" the number of occurrences is returned (not the index in such a case!)
